Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.54,0:01:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN E] You better give\Nus that map back or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--[explosion]\N--[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What... was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy fell from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY sighs]\NBut at least I'm safe now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...what just happened\Nto me was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"A Terrifying Mysterious Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy,\Nthe Clown Pirate."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[squeals]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NThey're all yours now, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN F]\NHey! That girl's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN D] That's okay.\NWe've got her boss now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN E]\NYou're in trouble, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You shoulda let your\Ncrony fend for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys know of anywhere\Ngood to eat around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Food's the least of\Nyour worries now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You better keep your\Nhands off my hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NYou bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they've\Nkilled that poor guy yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH yell, groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though both\Nof them had sabers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you beat them barehanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Hey! You're the\Ngirl who set me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a talented thief who\Nsteals strictly from pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Wanna team up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, thanks anyway, lady,\Nbut I think I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI stammers]\NHold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NAt least think about it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[stomach rumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, come with me and I'll\Nfind you something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NU-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] You're telling me they\Nstill haven't caught the thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN H]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But they should be in pursuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...right now, Captain... Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now explain to me, how in\Nthe world did she manage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to get her hands\Non that chart, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're preparing to\Nenter the Grand Line,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and go on a rampage,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then why wasn't the chart\Nproperly guarded?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The map was just sitting out,\Nplain as the nose on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY snorts]\NWhat did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean it was easy for\Nher to find and take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] Did you say\Nsomething about my nose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN H whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you trying to tell\Nme you find my nose funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my nose amusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir, you've misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you were quite clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN H whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN H]\NHelp me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... gonna use\Nthe Devil Fruit Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[choking]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, who am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN H choking]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain... Buggy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN H choking]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happens if\Nsomeone defies me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Flashy... death...\Nawaits... them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN H gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NQuit your groveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll overlook your slip-up\Nand forgive you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you better get\Nthat chart back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw up again... or else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NYes, Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you live in this big\Nhouse all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just staying here\Nfor the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's left this town\Nbecause of Captain Buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSo you're just a petty thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHow rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I only steal from people\Nwho deserve it: Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't compare me to\Nsome scumbag, petty thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A thief's a thief,\Nas far as I'm concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal is to earn a\Nhundred million berries,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how hard it is,\Nor how long it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need so many\Nberries for anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NIt's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But with this chart\Nof the Grand Line,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the hundred million is\Nnow a definite possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you must be a navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the most skilled navigator\Nyou're ever likely to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow. That's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about you join my crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking to\Nrecruit a navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be our\Nnewest crew member.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose this means\Nyou're a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a solemn promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised the guy who gave me\Nthis hat that I'd form a crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and become the\Ngreatest pirate ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that I despise\Nmore than pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I only like money\Nand tangerines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Be our navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN E]\NDid you find her or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN F]\NNo! I can't find her anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN E]\NWhere could she be hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN F]\NI don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're gonna\Nbe in big trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,if we don't get that chart back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NI gotta do something about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I might\Nconsider joining you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but only if you'll agree\Nto certain conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NReally? I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I want\Nyou to come with me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to pay a little visit to\NBuggy the pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to tie me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The rope's just for appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY chuckles]\NWell, okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking forward to\Nmeeting some other pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold your horses.\NWhat's the big rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me\Nthe thief got away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL] Please forgive us,\NCaptain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a more\Npathetic group than you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy, I have news!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NUgh. What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl who stole our chart\Nis back and with a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN muttering]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN E]\NIt's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the sneaky thief\Nwho stole the chart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] I've captured the thief,\NCaptain Buggy the Clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's your chart back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I don't\Nappreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the sudden change\Nof heart, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I had another fight\Nwith my boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just can't\Ntake it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd see if\NI could join your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY snorts, growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ca-Captain Buggy sure does\Nlook angry, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna use the\NDevil Fruit Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY snorting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fed up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I must admit,\Nyou're an amusing girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you! Of course\Nyou can join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] I've successfully\Ninfiltrated them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are so dumb and\Neasy to manipulate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, why am I in a cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great day to be a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl, what do you call yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's have a welcome\Nparty for our new friend Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're throwing this party\Nin your honor, so eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the party,\NCaptain Buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NI'll just keep my eyes peeled
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for a chance to take\Nback that chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll swipe all of Buggy's\Ntreasure, too, while I'm at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it... Almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is such a flashy party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Men, it's time to\Nprepare the Buggy Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN J snickering]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN J]\NAll set, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you\Ndoing with that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just observe, the awesome\Nmight of the Buggy Ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one heck\Nof an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:12:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like it was one of the\NCaptain's beloved Buggy Balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Buggy Balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was flashy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,With these Buggy Balls\Nand my Devil Fruit Powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have no problem\Nconquering the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,--[NAMI gasps]\N--[BUGGY] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's my destiny to\Nconquer the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'm gonna become\NKing of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] I can see why\Nyou're sick of him, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He never takes\Nanything seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,thinks that life's a big game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He acts like a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,--[NAMI laughs]\N--[BUGGY] I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] Then how about\NI give you a Buggy Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to blow away your old boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a great opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to prove your loyalty\Nto me, your new captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to finish\Nhim off quite yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get back to the welcoming\Nparty and just have more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my idea\Nof having more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NFire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Fire! Fire!\NFire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] If I don't shoot,\NI'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I do shoot, then I'm\Nno better than these pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Light the fuse, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NFire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BUGGY] Hey!\N--[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not wimping\Nout on me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hands are shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThat's what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,when you take on pirates\Nwith half-assed resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NResolve? To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To kill someone\Nlike it's nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a pirate's resolve?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NFire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be willing\Nto risk your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NFire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, new chick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit bein' sucha tease.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you how\Nto light the cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN I groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My mistake... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning\Nof this outrage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! Just\Nshoot him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So... now you've\Ndecided to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this\Nfor you, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want\Nto lower myself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to the level of these\Ninhuman pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates took the life of\Na person very dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! The fuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think pirates\Nare just inhuman filth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Get her, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN yelling, laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Water, water,\Nwater, water, water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh. Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--[HENCHMEN yelling]\N--[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[thud]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:17:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not very nice of you guys\Nto gang up on the poor girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NYou hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI said, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NUh, no, I'm fine, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhew, what a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you found us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hurry up and come\Nget me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] How do keep getting\Nyourself into these situations?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,First a bird flies off with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I find you\Ntrapped in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] It's an\Ninteresting story, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... That little brat\Njust called him Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThe crew he mentioned earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...was the Pirate Hunter Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NSo you're Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NIf you're here for my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got quite a\Nstruggle before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave up pirate hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here for my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm interested, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:18:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing you would\Nbolster my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to warn you,\Nbut oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--[HENCHMEN cheering]\N--[HENCHMAN J] Get 'em, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN K]\NYou can do it, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NBuggy! Buggy! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!\NBuggy! Buggy! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[snickers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY yelling, laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NDie flashily!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't much of\Na fight, now was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's weak! Way to go, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--[HENCHMEN laugh]\N--[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are they laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Their captain is lying\Ndead on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet they're still laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NFellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you find so damn funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--[thud]\N--[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Buggy's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat the... hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NThe Chop-Chop Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the name of the Devil\NFruit that's given me my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Chop-Chop person,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I can never be\Ndefeated by the sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His limbs... reattach?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always thought that the\NDevil Fruits were just a story
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that Pirates told.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's a Chop-Chop man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty freaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hit any vital organs,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's a serious\Nwound you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm guessing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,--...that I am the winner!\N--[HENCHMEN] Buggy! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BUGGY laughs]\N--Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NOh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The tables have turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't do something quick,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,they're gonna kill\Nall three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NBuggy! Buggy! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stabbing him in the back was\Na cowardly move, you Big Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NYou idiot! Don't call him that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's got a big nose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NBuggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY snorts]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kick your ass soon\Nas I get out of this cage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You kick my ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a lot of nerve, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm afraid all three of you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,are going to die here\Ntoday, by my own hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're going to\Ndo any ass kicking,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you better do it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done for. It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI refuse to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You better have a really good\Nplan or else we're all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you guys gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NNothing makes sense anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I hate pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NImpudent fool! Time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] Your Three-Sword\NStyle has no effect on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you I'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Listen when\NI'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BUGGY screams]\N--[HENCHMEN gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, the cannon's\Npointed at us! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHurry! Light it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--Do it now!\N--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The cannon's still loaded\Nwith a special Buggy Ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.62,0:22:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go out like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.41,0:22:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Done in by my own balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] I can't believe\Nyou just did that,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:22:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you ungrateful little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:22:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.17,0:23:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,N-N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.30,0:23:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.31,0:23:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.06,0:23:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.97,0:23:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.85,0:24:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.07,0:24:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.46,0:24:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou okay, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NYeah, don't worry. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.71,0:24:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.34,0:24:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NWhat're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.38,0:24:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't possibly be better!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.84,0:24:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.55,0:24:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NOh no! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.76,0:24:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhat an unfriendly little dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.55,0:24:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NI'm not referring to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.68,0:24:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Oh! There's a\Npolar bear on top of a lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.02,0:24:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThey followed you guys here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.14,0:24:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.98,0:24:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Desperate Situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.44,0:24:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast Tamer Mohji vs. Luffy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.90,0:24:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

